      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/ac/sqa",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "FEA software (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) operates under an FDA-recognized quality management system (ISO 13485-compliant). Software validation records, version control logs, and regression test suite results are archived. Required: documented QMS with version-controlled solver; achieved: full ISO 13485 QMS with automated regression testing across 47 benchmark cases."
      },
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is deployed under DePuy Synthes ISO 13485-certified QMS. Version control via Git with tagged release 2022.R2.SP1. Regression test suite of 47 NAFEMS benchmark cases executed at each release; all pass within 0.5% tolerance. FDA 21 CFR Part 11-compliant audit trail maintained. Software validation report SQA-2022-047 archived in document management system.",
      "evidence": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/evidence/sqa-report-2022-047"
    },
    {
